# CSV Explorer

A lightweight, browser-based CSV viewer and analyzer that allows users to upload, explore, search, filter, sort, and inspect CSV files without requiring a backend server or database.

All processing happens locally in the browser, ensuring fast performance and improved data privacy.

---

## Features

### 📂 CSV File Upload

* Upload CSV files directly from your device
* Client-side file processing
* Display uploaded file information

### 🔍 Global Search

* Search across all rows and columns
* Real-time filtering while typing
* Case-insensitive search

### 🎯 Advanced Filtering

* Create filters for individual columns
* Multiple filters can be applied simultaneously
* View active filter count
* Clear single or all filters instantly

### ↕️ Sorting

* Sort data in ascending or descending order
* Sort by any available column
* Visual indication of active sorting state

### 👁️ Column Management

* Show or hide columns dynamically
* Search within column names
* Reset column visibility settings

### 📊 Data Analysis

* Display total rows and columns
* Detect column data types:

  * Text
  * Number
  * Date
  * URL
  * Other

### 🗂️ Data Visualization

* Card-based data display
* Pagination support
* Adjustable items per page

### 🌙 Theme Support

* Light Mode
* Dark Mode
* Persistent theme preference

---

## Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)

No external libraries or frameworks are required.

